FYI I already fixed the activation issue of the generator (it should have been LeakyReLU) in [this commit](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/23035/commits/db6c86cffa294c7e35e9f81e6f92a7a53b3a531c). It might be easier if I just fix the text regarding the input noise input distribution in my PR #23035 if that's the only change, or you can PR against my branch.
